title: Heather Dubrow's Birthday Celebration Was a Dinner Fit for a Queen - Bravo (blog)
text:
More Your browser does not support iframes. 
Heather Dubrow deserves a big glass of Champs. The Real Housewives of Orange County podcaster celebrated her birthday on Thursday with a family-and-fun-filled dinner. 
Heather's husband, Terry Dubrow , and their four children, Max , Nicky, Kat, and Coco, gathered to wish the matriarch of the family a happy birthday, along with Terry's mother. The family donned cute, glittery crowns with Heather, the Birthday Queen, wearing the biggest one of them all. The Dubrows also munched on a delish-looking white cake decorated with flowers and bees. "Amazing birthday dinner ... family, food, love, champs, cards, gifts, hugs, kisses," Heather captioned a pic of the celebration on Instagram. A photo posted by Heather Dubrow (@heatherdubrow) on Jan 5, 2017 at 8:56pm PST
